				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nh%C6%B0/Ai-Nh%E1%BB%8B-Th%E1%BA%BF-ph%C3%BA/poem-nHHf8iIeresXmdhEV-ABLA">Ai Nhị Thế phú - 哀二世賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nh%C6%B0/author-HC1oHxsir20vL_KcVXiEhQ">Tư Mã Tương Như</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Di%E1%BB%85m/Bi-ph%E1%BA%ABn-thi/poem-d-K5myQmQMd-x20ZH01L_w">Bi phẫn thi - 悲憤詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Di%E1%BB%85m/author-EhbmJp2hi9HLiXQfO6maGA">Thái Diễm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-V%C5%A9/Bi%E1%BB%87t-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-03AO9JqLTWYZP_UYmalL6w">Biệt thi kỳ 1 - 別詩其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-V%C5%A9/author-A1qWp2TVE713T9GYde49XQ">Tô Vũ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0m-D%E1%BB%A5ng-Chi/Di-%C4%91i%E1%BA%BFu-ng%C6%B0-L%C3%BD-x%E1%BB%AD-s%C4%A9/poem-tH0AFryxbOx5NYPInO_Izw">Di điếu ngư Lý xử sĩ - 貽釣魚李處士</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0m-D%E1%BB%A5ng-Chi/author-k_4EEx6yQhcGl5XMaCdIaA">Đàm Dụng Chi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-Th%E1%BB%ABa-Trinh/%C4%90%C3%A1p-T%E1%BB%91ng-Chi-V%E1%BA%A5n/poem-ktB77dJe3tTRJiVsLhIreQ">Đáp Tống Chi Vấn - 答宋之問</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-Th%E1%BB%ABa-Trinh/author-rERhvQ4Diy8h_kyNo6zqVg">Tư Mã Thừa Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/Ho%E1%BA%A1-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-S%C6%A1n-M%E1%BB%99ng-S%C6%A1n-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-lan-ch%E1%BA%BF-sinh-v%C3%A3n-t%E1%BB%AB-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-sxn8C2ATwfk0moNepNgjqQ">Hoạ Hương Sơn Mộng Sơn đình tương lan chế sinh vãn từ nguyên vận - 和香山梦山亭湘籣製生輓詞原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.th